# Scope discipline

- Prefer the smallest correct change; do not refactor unrelated code.
- Do not add training implementation unless the task is Wave A / execute phase.
- Do not re-introduce removed tooling (e.g. validate scripts) unless explicitly requested.
- Match existing naming, layout, and documentation level in the template.
